docs {
  # Create a new project (US3)
  
  Creates a new project. The creator automatically becomes an ADMIN member.
  
  ## Example projects:
  - PMT - Application Mobile
  - PMT - Backend API
  - PMT - Frontend Web
  - Sprint 1 - Authentification
  - Refactoring Base de données
  
  ## Request body:
  - **name**: Project name (2-100 characters, required)
  - **description**: Project description (max 2000 characters)
  - **startDate**: Start date in YYYY-MM-DD format (required)
  - **createdByUserId**: ID of the user creating the project (required)
  
  ## Response:
  - **201 Created**: Project successfully created
  - **400 Bad Request**: Validation error
  - **404 Not Found**: User not found
}
